item.description:
Floyd Patterson returns to Shaker Farms
right now I don't have much information about this, but I did want to get it posted. It will most likely again be a dinner buffet and dancing for $25 per person. We've had some great fun here at Shaker Farms and we all know how good this band is.

As we get closer and I get more information I will post updates.........

Organized by
Al Cardaropoli from the Spice of Life's Too Short meetup group
Floyd Patterson
item.how_to_find_us: Maybe meetup at Chili's in West Springfield and go over to Shaker as a group/pack/mob/dance troupe
item.why: We had such a good time last time (we closed the place down)
item.name: Floyd Patterson is Back
